<item>
 <title>Video: Scorpions for Dinner</title>
 <link>http://theworldisnotflat.com/scorpions</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt; I&#039;m not sure what I&#039;ve gotten myself into with this whole concept eating strange things in foreign countries, but the ball is rolling... downhill. I fear that I may not be able to top this one.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;object width=&quot;425&quot; height=&quot;350&quot;&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;movie&quot; value=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/v/lD1lMq-KyPY&quot;&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;embed src=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/v/lD1lMq-KyPY&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; width=&quot;425&quot; height=&quot;350&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, yes, I know a scorpion is an arachnid and not an insect.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;clear&quot; /&gt;</description>
